{"tid":2411210,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"准黎智英保釋遭建制派狂轟 司法機構特首辦拒透露李運騰是否已被DQ","createTime":"2021-02-17T07:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T07:55:14.000Z","uid":44209,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c86d5f80e9d1adc0bb258ed2150d72988f1ccd0a","tid":2411210,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2FdiApz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2FdiApz.png&h=c375af70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n終審法院早前裁定，高等法院法官李運騰錯誤詮釋《國安法》條文，因此宣佈其批准壹傳媒創辦人黎智英保釋的決定無效。高院將於明日（18日）處理黎再次提出的保釋申請，但改由法官彭寶琴負責。司法機構及特首辦回覆《蘋果》查詢時，拒絕透露李運騰是否已被取消「指定法官」資格，亦無解釋為何李運騰沒有繼續處理此案。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/FY6COEAB6ZHFVI6WWU2H5NJWNE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2FFY6COEAB6ZHFVI6WWU2H5NJWNE%2F&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN28WiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=5e414db7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2FFY6COEAB6ZHFVI6WWU2H5NJWNE%2F&h=3a110fec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/FY6COEAB6ZHFVI6WWU2H5NJWNE/</a>"},{"pid":"666c41c93e9412cea2a08a0b0d75da1422c015de","tid":2411210,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:26:15.000Z","msg":"做狗官做到俾狗咬, 失鳩敗到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6149f78a53689cf12b0a5d1e9793e7fd2d0c72a","tid":2411210,"uid":14867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:26:28.000Z","msg":"國安法解錯就DQ，拎刀斬人讚關心社會就低調了事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67703a2389a452af2404b3d7961730140ba26a0f","tid":2411210,"uid":